{"tid":232000,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]《俺妹》推出綾瀬線結局小說","createTime":"2017-05-06T12:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T23:12:47.000Z","uid":102208,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea7b255b1312c53e51594e5b210a053d603bcf0","tid":232000,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"4月新番《情色漫畫老師》作者前作輕小說《我的妹妹不可能那麼可愛》番外綾瀨線製作決定！<br />\n<br />\n《我的妹妹哪有這麼可愛！》這本小說還有動畫雖然最後都是走實妹線，但是在當年俺妹的改編PSP遊戲有京介和不同的女主角結婚生子的結局，亦即是if線的故事<br />\n而今天《我的妹妹哪有這麼可愛！》宣佈將推出由伏見司親自加筆修正的俺妹綾瀨線結局小說，在這個綾瀨線的結局中綾瀬與京介成為了夫妻還生下了一個可愛的女兒，綾瀬黨大翻身！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vh901Xn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVh901Xn.jpg&h=f4b7c2a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 綾瀬黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hkacger.com/archives/38671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F38671&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=8a7f7f96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkacger.com/archives/38671</a>"},{"pid":"3f0dacb485fa6cf3c6015bb27551c149d507535f","tid":232000,"uid":72127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nBtw成套書扔曬了"},{"pid":"2b5f6d3a5c62195be61c2511dbfdd63f362b7555","tid":232000,"uid":63792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"媽我最期待的畫面出現了"},{"pid":"8306d478b98b41e0e0a9f5a1939ba873069f9bc4","tid":232000,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:51:24.000Z","msg":"⛩"},{"pid":"da22c827e38aa1a9029931ef7e8aa78dad2118df","tid":232000,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl